• We see that $\{W_{K}^{(t)},W_{Q}^{(t)}\}_{t=0}^{\infty}$ satisfies A2 by construction;   
• Since this is a dynamics with LayerNorm, applying $W_{V}^{(t)}$ is in fact equivalent to applying   
$\hat{W}_{V}=W_{V}/\lVert W_{V}\rVert_{2}$ under the dynamics, where the latter has 2-norm at most 1 and thus using $\hat{W}_{V}$ satisfies A3.
